Fazail and Adab -e- Gasht

Mere Mohtarum buzurgo aur azizi bhaiyo Allah swt ka bahot bada
ahsan hai karam hai fazal hai Allah swt ne hame magrib ki namaaz 
baa jammat padhne ki taufiq ata farmayi

Mere Mohtarum buzurgo aur azizi bhaiyo hame sab ho abhi jo mehnat 
krni hai woh gasht wali mehnat hai

Mere Mohtarum buzurgo aur azizi bhaiyo jab bhi ummat
mein bigaad aata Allah swt nabi bhejte nabi deen ki 
mehnat krte log deen par chalte .Nabi jaane ke baad log
fir islam se hat jaate. Fir Allah swt nabi bhejte.
Fir Allah swt ne hamare aur aapke rasool Muhammed swa ko duniya mein bheja

Mere Mahutaram buzurgo aur azizi bhaiyo Adam As se lekar 
jitne bhi ambiya is duniya mein aaye un sabi ambiya 
ne ye gasth wal mehnat ki. Hamare aur aap ke rasool 
Muhammed swa ne bhi ye mehnat ki thi.

Gasht krna tamman ambiya ki sunnat hai

Agar koi chahe ki tamman ambiya ki sunnat ko zinda
kre to gasht ke zariye se kr skta hai

Ab koi nabi nhi aane wala. Ab ye zimmedari Allah swt 
ne ham par daali hai. Ab ham sab ko milkar yeh gasht 
ki mehnat krni hai.

Ye itna ucha amal hai jis mein 1 qadam pr 700 gunah 
amaal naame se mitaye jayenge, 700 nekiyah amaal naame 
mein likhe jaayenge aur jannat me 700 darjat buland
honge.

1 subahAllah kehne pr 7 lakh subanAllah kehne ka sawab
milenga


Agar Allah swt kisi basti mein azaab bhejne chahe aur
wah gasht ki mehnat hoti to Allah tala us azaab ko 
mansookh kr dete hai

